GENERAL README AND INSTALLED PACKAGES AND NOTES

general links: https://wq2012.github.io/awesome-diarization/#Other-software


########
pyannote
########

need speechbrain==0.5.12 i think? (check version, one of them breaks pyannote)

pip3 install https://github.com/pyannote/pyannote-audio/archive/develop.zip
pip3 install speechbrain




##################
speech recognition
##################

https://realpython.com/python-speech-recognition/

pip3 install SpeechRecognition




##########
deepspeech
##########


can't use python 3.10

for instillation go to docs from gtihub, 

https://github.com/mozilla/DeepSpeech
https://deepspeech.readthedocs.io/en/r0.9/?badge=latest

pip3 install deepspeech
pip3 install --upgrade deepspeech
wget https://github.com/mozilla/DeepSpeech/releases/download/v0.9.3/deepspeech-0.9.3-models.pbmm
wget https://github.com/mozilla/DeepSpeech/releases/download/v0.9.3/deepspeech-0.9.3-models.scorer

the wgets are fat, dont add to git!





##################
audio file editing
##################


use pydub https://www.geeksforgeeks.org/working-with-wav-files-in-python-using-pydub/

pip3 install pydub
sudo apt/yum install ffmpeg (requirement aparently! -> maybe conda install would fix it)

